title: Black Celebs With Blue, Green & Hazel Eyes
text:
Black America Web Featured Video CLOSE Beauty comes in countless forms, especially when it comes to black folks—the race that can arguably produce the most wide-range of skin tones.
One striking trait that seems to often stand out is the presence of light-colored eyes…It’s been said that it challenges long-standing stereotypes and expands the narrative of what black beauty looks like. Whether piercing blue, mesmerizing green, or warm haze, these eye colors undoubtedly add an unforgettable allure to these celebrities’ overall appearance.
